'''Coruscani Publishing''' was a publishing house located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. They were famous for their non-fiction literature.<ref name="The Smugglers of Naboo">{{Wizards|url=starwars/article.asp?x=rpg_fastPlay_intro|text=The Smugglers of Naboo|int=The Smugglers of Naboo}}</ref> It published the anthology "''[[Lyrical Metaphysics: Ode on an Odon]]''" by the [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorian]] [[Soshu Londahl]].<ref name="Life's Memories article">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/livingforce/swlf20030703memories|text=Life's Memories}}</ref>

